Package gov.ca.water.calgui

Main package for CalLite GUI.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CalLiteHelp Generates help window allowing search of Cal-Lite user's manual.
CalLiteSplash Loads custom splash screen for CalLite GUI
FileAction The FileAction class is the action listener for menubar "menu" and panel "runsettings" in the GUI.
FileDialog Supports selection of different types of CalLite files from customized JFileChoosers.
MainMenu Main class for CalLite GUI.
RunUtils The RunUtils class contains the necessary methods for doing a single, batch, or WSIDI run.
ScenarioMonitor Tracks and displays scenario status during save and run
SpinnerSetup Sets up Spinner models for number range, months
 

Package gov.ca.water.calgui Description

Main package for CalLite GUI. See MainMenu.main() for main routine.
